comments: Dani is one of the most incredible educators from which you could ever hope to learn. You will work your ass off, but the knowledge you earn is so worth it. She expects the best on papers but will help you get there every step of the way.
Dani is incredibly intelligent, and cares deeply about her students. She will push you to your limits (especially with papers), but she won\'t let you drown.

You read read read and discuss discuss discuss. But it\'s all worth it. She is amazing at being patient while you figure out what you want to do with your life/write a paper about. She\'s pretty much the bomb.
Yeah you have to read until you drop dead, but it\'s worth it. She\'s passionate and goes above her duties to help you figure out what to do with your life. That\'s pretty sweet.
